quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,"Tuma nde feddeeji …ói…ói e mo'on himmu no, nde cooyato, ko Alla non woni Gi…óo ma…ď…ďe. Ko Alla woni ko goŇč…óim…ďe …ďen haani hoolorde."
  3,123,"GooŇč…óii Alla Wallii on √Īande Badri, tawi ko on hoy…ďe. Kulee Alla, belajo'o on yettay [Mo]."
  3,124,"Nde maakanayno…óaa gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen: "Enee, yonaŇčtaa on nde Joomi mo'on …ďeydanta on Malaa'ikaa…ďe guluuje tato jippinaa…ďe?"."
  3,125,"Pellet, si on mu√Ī√Īike on gom…óii, e arday on hawjere ma…ď…ďe, …óum …óoo, Joomi mo'on no ∆Āeydira on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandinaa…ďe."
  3,126,"Alla Wa…óiraani …óum si wanaa wewlere wonannde on, e no …ďer…óe mon …óen …óee∆īira …óum. Ballal iwrataa si wanaa ka Alla, On poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo."
  3,127,"Ko fii yo O tay∆īu fedde e …ďen yeddu…ďe maa O Wirta …ďe, …ďe nduttoo ko …ďe sooyu…ďe."
  3,128,"Laatanaaki ma e fiyaake on hay e huunde : maa O Ja…ďan …ďe tuubuubuyee, maa O Lepto …ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe too√Īoo…ďe."
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana on mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko Haforoowo Yurmetee…óo."
  3,130,"Hey mon yo goŇč…óim…ďe, wata on √Īaamu ribaa, cowalle sowaa…óe. Kulee Alla, belajo'o, on malete."
  3,131,"kulee ngen yiite maranaange …ďen heefer…ďe."
  3,132,"∆äoftee Alla e Nulaa…óo on, belajo'o, on njurmete."